\c 25
\s Ilizwe lakoJuda lizakuba yinkangala okweminyaka engamatshumi ayisikhombisa
\p
\v 1 Ilizwi elafika kuJeremiya mayelana labantu bonke bakoJuda, ngomnyaka wesine kaJehoyakhimi indodana kaJosiya, inkosi yakoJuda\x + 1.3; 36.1. 2 Kho. 24.1. Dan. 1.1.\x* (kwakungumnyaka wokuqala kaNebhukadirezari, inkosi yeBhabhiloni),
\v 2 alikhulumayo uJeremiya umprofethi kubo bonke abantu bakoJuda, lakubo bonke abahlali beJerusalema, esithi:
\v 3 Kusukela emnyakeni wetshumi lantathu kaJosiya, indodana kaAmoni, inkosi yakoJuda,\x + 1.2.\x* kuze kube lamuhla, sekuyiminyaka engamatshumi amabili lantathu, ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lifikile kimi, njalo ngilikhulumile kini, ngivuka ngovivi ngikhuluma;\x + 2 Lan. 36.15.\x* kodwa kalilalelanga.\x + 6.17; 7.13; 11.7,8,10; 13.10,11; 16.12; 17.23; 18.12; 19.15; 22.21; 25.4,7,8; 26.5; 29.19; 34.14; 35.15.\x*
\v 4 Futhi iN\nd kosi\nd* ithumile kini zonke izinceku zayo, abaprofethi, ivuka ngovivi i\add ba\add*thuma;\x + 2 Lan. 36.15.\x* kodwa kalilalelanga,\x + 6.17; 7.13; 11.7,8,10; 13.10,11; 16.12; 17.23. 18.12; 19.15; 22.21; 25.4,7,8; 26.5; 29.19; 34.14; 35.15.\x* kalibekanga indlebe yenu ukuthi lizwe;\x + 7.26; 11.8; 17.23; 34.14; 35.15.\x*
\v 5 besithi: Phendukani khathesi ngulowo lalowo\x + 18.11.\x* endleleni yakhe embi,\x + 4.4; 23.22.\x* lebubini bezenzo zenu,\x + 4.4; 23.22.\x* lihlale elizweni iN\nd kosi\nd* elinike lina laboyihlo\x + 7.7.\x* kusukela nininini kuze kube nininini;\x + 7.7.\x*
\v 6 njalo lingalandeli abanye onkulunkulu ukubasebenzela lokubakhonza,\x + 7.6; 13.10; 35.15. Dute. 6.14.\x* lingangithukuthelisi\x + 7.18. Dute. 32.21.\x* ngomsebenzi wezandla zenu;\x + 1.16.\x* khona ngingayikulenzela okubi.
\v 7 Kodwa kalingilalelanga, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, ukuze lingithukuthelise\x + 7.18. Dute. 32.21.\x* ngomsebenzi wezandla zenu, kuze kube kubi kini.\x + 1.16.\x*
