\v 8 Ngakho itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla: Ngenxa yokuthi lingawalalelanga amazwi ami,
\v 9 khangela, ngizathuma, ngilande zonke izinsapho zenyakatho,\x + 1.13,15.\x* itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, lakuNebhukadirezari inkosi yeBhabhiloni inceku yami, ngibalethe bamelane lalelilizwe\x + 27.6; 40.2; 43.10. Isa. 44.28; 45.1. Hez. 29.18,19,20.\x* bamelane labakhileyo balo, bamelane lazo zonke lezizizwe inhlangothi zonke,\x + 25.9; 27.3,6; 28.14.\x* ngibatshabalalise, ngibenze babe yisesabiso,\x + 4.7; 18.16; 25.18.\x* babe ngokuncifelwayo,\x + 4.7; 18.16; 25.18.\x* babe zincithakalo ezilaphakade.
\v 10 Futhi ngizaphelisa ngisuse kubo ilizwi lentokozo lelizwi lenjabulo, ilizwi lomyeni lelizwi likamakoti,\x + 7.34. Isa. 24.6,7,8,9,10,11,12.\x* umsindo wamatshe okuchola,\x + Tshu. 12.4. Eks. 11.5.\x*\x + Isam. 18.22,23.\x* lokukhanya kwesibane.\x + Isam. 18.22,23.\x*
\v 11 Lelizwe lonke leli lizakuba lunxiwa\x + 22.5; 25.18.\x* libe yisesabiso;\x + 4.7; 18.16; 25.18.\x* lalezizizwe zizasebenzela inkosi yeBhabhiloni\x + 25.9; 27.3,6; 28.14.\x* iminyaka engamatshumi ayisikhombisa.\x + Isa. 23.15.\x*
\v 12 Kuzakuthi-ke iminyaka engamatshumi ayisikhombisa isiphelele\x + 27.7,22; 29.10. 2 Lan. 36.21,22. Ezra 1.1. Dan. 9.2. Zek. 1.12; 7.5.\x* ngijezise inkosi yeBhabhiloni lalesosizwe, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, \add ngo\add*bubi babo, lelizwe lamaKhaladiya, ngilenze libe ngamanxiwa laphakade.\x + 25.9; 50.3,13,23,39,40,45; 51.26,62. Hez. 35.9. Zef. 2.9. Isa. 13.19; 14.23; 21.1; 47.1.\x*
\v 13 Ngehlisele phezu kwalelolizwe wonke amazwi ami engawakhuluma ngimelene lalo, konke okubhaliweyo kulolugwalo,\x + Jer.46; Jer. 51.\x* uJeremiya akuprofethayo ngazo zonke izizwe.
\v 14 Ngoba izizwe ezinengi\x + 27.7; 30.8.\x*\x + 50.9,41; 51.27,28.\x* lamakhosi amakhulu\x + 27.7; 30.8.\x*\x + 50.9,41; 51.27,28.\x* zizabasebenzisa bona uqobo;\x + 27.7; 30.8.\x*\x + 22.13. Levi 25.39.\x* njalo ngizabaphindisela njengokwenza kwabo\x + 50.29; 51.6,24.\x* lanjengokomsebenzi wezandla zabo.
